Package com.vmware.nsx_policy.global_infra.domains

Class DomainsFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_policy.global_infra.domains.DomainsFactory
  • public class DomainsFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    DomainsFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx_policy.global_infra.domains package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
